\c 34
\s UElihu uvikela ukulunga kukaNkulunkulu
\p
\v 1 Wasephendula uElihu wathi\x + Hlu. 18.14.\x*:
\v 2 Zwanini amazwi ami, zihlakaniphi, lani zazi, libeke indlebe kimi.
\v 3 Ngoba indlebe ihlola amazwi, njengolwanga lunambitha ukudla\x + 12.11.\x*.
\v 4 Asizikhetheleni isahlulelo; sazi phakathi kwethu okuhle\x + 1 Thes. 5.21.\x*.
\v 5 Ngoba uJobe uthe: Ngilungile\x + 13.18. 33.9.\x*, kodwa uNkulunkulu ususe isahlulelo sami\x + 27.2.\x*;
\v 6 ngiqamba amanga ngimelene lelungelo lami\x + 9.17,20.\x*; umtshoko wami kawelapheki, ngaphandle kwesiphambeko\x + 33.9.\x*.
\v 7 Nguwuphi umuntu onjengoJobe? Unatha ukuklolodelwa njengamanzi\x + 15.16.\x*,
\v 8 ahambahambe exukwini labenzi bobubi, ahambe labantu benkohlakalo.
\v 9 Ngoba uthe\x + 9.22,23. 21.7,15. 24.1.\x*: Kakumsizi umuntu nxa ethokoza ngoNkulunkulu\x + 22.2.\x*.
\v 10 Ngakho, bantu bengqondo, ngilalelani: Kakube khatshana loNkulunkulu\x + 27.5.\x* ukwenza inkohlakalo\x + 8.3. Roma 9.14.\x*, loSomandla ukwenza isiphambeko\x + 36.23. Dute. 32.4. 2 Lan. 19.7. Hlab. 92.15.\x*.
\v 11 Ngoba umsebenzi womuntu uzawubuyisela kuye\x + Hlab. 62.12.\x*, amenze athole njengendlela yalowo lalowo\x + Jer. 17.10. 32.19.\x*.
\v 12 Yebo, isibili uNkulunkulu kenzi okubi, njalo uSomandla kagobisi isehlulelo\x + 8.3.\x*.
\v 13 Ngubani owambeka phezu komhlaba\x + 36.23. Nani 4.27. Ezra 1.2.\x*? Kumbe ngubani owamisa umhlaba wonke\x + 38.5.\x*?
\v 14 Uba ebeka inhliziyo yakhe phezu kwakhe\x + 2.3.\x*, uzabuthela\x + Hlab. 104.29.\x* umoya wakhe lomphefumulo wakhe kuye\x + 32.8.\x*.
\v 15 Inyama yonke ibizaphela kanyekanye\x + Hlab. 104.29.\x*, lomuntu abuyele ethulini\x + 10.9. Gen. 3.19. Hlab. 146.4. Tshu. 12.7.\x*\x + Hlab. 104.29.\x*.
\v 16 Uba kulokuqedisisa-ke, zwana lokhu, ubeke indlebe elizwini lamazwi ami\x + 33.1.\x*.
\v 17 Kambe, ozonda isehlulelo ubengabusa yini? Kambe uzamlahla yini olungileyo kakhulu\x + Gen. 18.25.\x*?
\v 18 Angatsho yini enkosini\x + Eks. 22.28.\x*: Mkhohlisi; kuziphathamandla: \add Lina\add* abangelaNkulunkulu\x + 2 Sam. 23.6.\x*?
\v 19 \add Kuye\add* ongemukeli ubuso beziphathamandla\x + 42.8. Dute. 10.17.\x*, engananzi isinothi phambi komyanga\x + Jak. 2.5.\x*? Ngoba bonke bangumsebenzi wezandla zakhe\x + 31.15.\x*.
\v 20 Bayafa ngesikhatshana\x + 21.13.\x*; laphakathi kobusuku abantu bayaqhuqhiswa, bedlule\x + 36.20. Eks. 11.4.12. 29,30.\x*; kuzasuswa olamandla kungelasandla\x + Dan. 8.25.\x*.
\v 21 Ngoba amehlo akhe aphezu kwendlela zomuntu\x + 2 Lan. 16.9.\x*, uyabona zonke izinyathelo zakhe\x + 14.16. 18.7. 31.4,37.\x*.
\v 22 Kakulamnyama\x + Hlab. 139.12.\x* njalo kakulathunzi lokufa lapho abenzi bobubi abangacatsha khona\x + 3.5.\x*.
\v 23 Ngoba kabi lokhu enaka umuntu, ukuthi aye kuNkulunkulu esahlulelweni.
\v 24 Uyaphahlaza abalamandla kungahlolwanga, amise abanye endaweni zabo\x + 8.19. Isa. 65.15.\x*.
\v 25 Ngakho uyayazi imisebenzi yabo, uya\add ba\add*genqula\x + Zaga 12.7.\x* ebusuku, bachotshozwe\x + 34.20. 27.20. 36.20.\x*.
\v 26 Uyabatshaya njengababi endaweni yababukelayo\x + 27.23.\x*.
\v 27 Ngenxa yokuthi bephambukile ekumlandeleni, bengananzanga leyodwa yezindlela zakhe\x + Hlab. 64.9. Hlab. 28.5. Isa. 5.12.\x*,
\v 28 baze benza ukukhala komyanga kufike kuye\x + 35.9. Jak. 5.4.\x*, njalo wakuzwa ukukhala kwabahluphekayo\x + Eks. 22.23.\x*.
\v 29 Lapho yena ethulisa, ngubani-ke ongaziphatha ngenkohliso\x + Hlab. 94.13.\x*? Lapho efihla ubuso, ngubani-ke ongambona\x + 33.26.\x*? Loba esizweni loba emuntwini eyedwa.
\v 30 Ukuze abantu abangabazenzisi bangabusi, ukuze bangabi yimijibila ebantwini\x + 1 Kho. 12.28,30. 2 Kho. 21.9.\x*.
\v 31 Isibili uthe kuNkulunkulu: Ngithwele \add isijeziso\x + Hos. 13.1.\x*\add*, kangiyikona\x + 24.9. Neh. 1.7.\x*.
\v 32 Lokhu engingakuboniyo ngifundise wena; uba ngenze okubi kangisayikukwenza futhi\x + Hlab. 19.12. 90.8.\x*.
\v 33 Uzaphindisela yini njengokuthanda kwakho, loba uyala, loba wena ukhetha, njalo kungesimi? Wazini-ke? Khuluma\x + 33.32.\x*.
\v 34 Abantu abalokuqedisisa bazakhuluma kimi, lomuntu ohlakaniphileyo uzangizwa.
\v 35 UJobe ukhulume engelalwazi, lamazwi akhe kawalanhlakanipho\x + 35.16.\x*.
\v 36 Kungathi ngabe uJobe uyahlolwa kuze kube sekupheleni, ngenxa yempendulo \add zakhe\add* njengabantu ababi.
\v 37 Ngoba esonweni sakhe wengezelela ububi, etshaya izandla phakathi kwethu, esandisa amazwi akhe emelene loNkulunkulu\x + 27.23.\x*.
